<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Home' }) %>

<main>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-background"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tagline fade-in-up">Women-led journeys</p>
      <h1 class="fade-in-up delay-1">Discover Brazil<br>Through Local Eyes</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle fade-in-up delay-2">Where strangers become friends, and a trip becomes something that unfolds long after you return home.</p>
      <a href="/experience" class="btn btn-primary fade-in-up delay-3">Explore the Experience</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="section section-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro">
        <div class="intro-text">
          <p class="lead">"Sou feita de liberdade e desejo. Intensa."</p>
          <p>We are a group of Brazilian women who have found ourselves drawn to a particular calling: to serve as guides and companions for women venturing into Brazil.</p>
          <p>We help you discover not merely the postcard version of this vast country, but its deeper rhythms and textures. We offer entry into the living pulse of local culture—into those moments of connection and surprise that transform a trip into something that continues to unfold long after the return flight home.</p>
          <p>Brazil reveals itself not in grand gestures alone but in the small ceremonies of daily life: in the warmth of strangers who become friends, in the music that spills from doorways at dusk, in the way a shared meal becomes an act of intimacy.</p>
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Meet Your Guides</a>
        </div>
        <div class="intro-image">
          <img src="/images/RnFriends.png" alt="Women traveling together in Brazil" class="intro-photo">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="section section-sand">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What Makes This Different</h2>
        <p>This is not a tour. It's an invitation into our world.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">✦</div>
          <h3>Bespoke Journeys</h3>
          <p>Every trip is crafted around your group's interests, energy, and sense of adventure. No two journeys are the same.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">✦</div>
          <h3>Local Companionship</h3>
          <p>We're not tour operators—we're your friends in Brazil. We walk alongside you, sharing our communities and connections.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">✦</div>
          <h3>Women Together</h3>
          <p>There's something particular about how women travel together. We hold space for the conversations, trust, and connection that emerge.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section section-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2>Ready to Begin?</h2>
        <p>Tell us about your group, your dreams for this journey, and we'll start crafting something extraordinary together.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 2rem;">Start the Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
